highlights.text: Jin has the most spots on Top Songs Singapore. “Don’t Say You Love Me” is the highest at #1.
“你，好不好？ - TVBS連續劇【遺憾拼圖】片尾曲” by Eric Chou has been on Top Songs Singapore the longest, at 3142 days straight.
“A Little More” by Ed Sheeran is the highest new entry on Top Songs Singapore at #38.
“WANTCHU” by keshi is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Singapore, up 175 spots at #9.
